channel.title: Loading RSPS webclient error click here for details
channel.description:
My friend is hosting a rsps and its running pretty good for him. He has me and my other friend playing right now, but only my friend is playing. Everytime I try to load the webclient it gets pasted the spinning java stage thing, then after that it brings me to a white page and at the top left corner it says "Error, Click here for Details" what is happening?
I tried downloading the client and all when I extract the files it works so I when I play the client it just has this loud sound doesnt even load up. So if you have any idea's on that please help please.
PLEASE, I REALLY NEED HELP Anyone have any idea's to what is happening please let me know
